<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Banking System API Aldowad</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
    }

    .container {
      text-align: center;
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      max-width: 600px;
      width: 100%;
      box-sizing: border-box; 
    }


    p {
      color: #333;
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .btn-container {
      margin-top: 20px;
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .btn {
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      cursor: pointer;
      margin: 5px;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .btn-endpoint {
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .btn-user {
      background-color: #24ff7f;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .btn-documentation{
      background-color: rgb(255, 178, 36);
      color: #fff;
    }
    .btn-endpoint:hover {
      background-color: #0056b3;
    }

    .btn-user:hover {
      background-color: #0fb300;
    }
    .btn-documentation:hover {
      background-color: #b37a00;
    }
    

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      /* Adjust styles for mobile devices */
      .container {
        padding: 10px;
      }

      p {
        font-size: 16px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>
      Welcome to Banking System API
    </h1>
    <p>
      This is the main page of the Banking System API application.
      The application is based on the banking system,allowing you to perform secure CRUD operations using JsonWebToken.
      Utilizing Prisma to design the database, Express to handle the request, and Postgres for the database, the application features three main sections:
      Register, Login, and Dashboard. Users can also reset their passwords, and a template email will be sent to continue the process.
    </p>

    <div class="btn-container">
      <!-- Button for Endpoint Transaction -->
      <a href="https://dull-lime-elephant-cape.cyclic.app/transaction" class="btn btn-endpoint" target="_blank">Endpoint Transaction</a>
      
      <!-- Button for Endpoint User -->
      <a href="https://dull-lime-elephant-cape.cyclic.app/user" class="btn btn-endpoint" target="_blank">Endpoint User</a>

      <!-- Button for Endpoint Account Bank -->
      <a href="https://dull-lime-elephant-cape.cyclic.app/bank-account" class="btn btn-endpoint" target="_blank">Endpoint Account Bank</a>

      <!-- Button for User Actions - Register -->
      <a href="https://dull-lime-elephant-cape.cyclic.app/register" class="btn btn-user" target="_blank">Register</a>

      <!-- Button for User Actions - Login -->
      <a href="https://dull-lime-elephant-cape.cyclic.app/Login" class="btn btn-user" target="_blank">Login</a>

      <!-- Button for User docs - documentations -->
      <a href="https://dull-lime-elephant-cape.cyclic.app/docs/" class="btn btn-documentation" target="_blank">Documentations</a>
    </div>
    <h3>
      Developed by Aldowad Simanjuntak
    </h3>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
